      "content": "hey i just got prescribed zolpidem for sleeping but i'm having a hard time falling asleep with just the pill. i had a glass of wine with dinner tonight, do u think it's okay if i take my pill now? i feel like the wine might help it kick in faster so i can finally pass out",
